{"tid":871889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【永不放棄】日本女跑手接力賽意外骨折　跪爬 200 米交捧隊友 但亦有人質疑「這是在縮短運動員的生命」","createTime":"2018-10-22T10:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:05:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"362cb3888ff50515445627ac3279b3daa6712f33","tid":871889,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/RUN_arXFT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FRUN_arXFT_1200x0.png&h=e885c7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nyoutube 片段截圖<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/0bw7pG-Hw7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0bw7pG-Hw7c&d=ax1iBzcBQBHgfFlmKBArgO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=dd83ffd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0bw7pG-Hw7c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本田徑賽場發生動人一幕。昨日在福岡舉行第38次全日本職業隊女子長距離接力賽，代表「岩谷產業」的19歲女跑手飯田怜，在距離終點還有200多米時，和其他跑手碰撞受傷，她手纏著接力帶，雙膝跪著爬完最後約200公尺賽事交棒予隊友，沿途的觀眾和旁述都為她打氣。<br />\n<br />\n賽事每棒跑約10.6公里，4棒合共42公里，代表岩谷產業的飯田怜擔任第二棒，但在到交棒點前最後一個彎位和其他跑手碰撞後倒地，日本傳媒報道她原來是右腳脛骨骨折，需要休養3到4個月，但在嚴重傷勢下飯田怜未有放棄，雙膝跪著爬回接棒點，裁判和救護車緊跟著她，直到她完成賽事，她第三棒的隊友在等待時忍不住落淚。<br />\n<br />\n飯田怜最終爬回接棒點，將接力帶交予隊友後在路旁接受治療，除了骨折的右腳外，雙膝都因為爬行而血流如注，有網民就在片段留言「佩服她的堅持」，<strong>但亦有人質疑為何教練和主辦單位不阻止她，「這不是運動精神..這是在傷害自己縮短運動員的生命」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/sport/%E6%B0%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%B3%E8%B7%91%E6%89%8B%E6%8E%A5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B3%BD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E8%B7%AA%E7%88%AC-200-%E7%B1%B3%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A7%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25B7%2591%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%258A%2598-%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E7%2588%25AC-200-%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%258D%25A7%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%258B%2F&d=ax1iBzcBQBHgfFlmKBArgO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=5ca41886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25B7%2591%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%258A%2598-%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E7%2588%25AC-200-%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%258D%25A7%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%258B%2F&h=67b657d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/sport/%E6%B0%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%B3%E8%B7%91%E6%89%8B%E6%8E%A5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B3%BD%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E8%B7%AA%E7%88%AC-200-%E7%B1%B3%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A7%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起slamdunk ending"},{"pid":"6a878aa6e516229b47e82a04c18feafc1056448c","tid":871889,"uid":22137,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"明明可以單腳跳 做咩唔跳 咁樣爬仲傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368bb97b880ad5770dec38f6af7e1b1250c8d4b6","tid":871889,"uid":32342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"165但腳比例都幾長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b56910421d318c0861e18cccf3515535014632","tid":871889,"uid":58247,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6a878aa6e516229b47e82a04c18feafc1056448c","tid":871889,"uid":22137,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"明明可以單腳跳 做咩唔跳 咁樣爬仲傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:16:50.000Z","msg":"父子騎驢"},{"pid":"96da73bbd5f0b1c45fd1c260455f3efdb2d153f2","tid":871889,"uid":22137,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9b56910421d318c0861e18cccf3515535014632","tid":871889,"uid":58247,"l